des:
for example, youou set the feeder device name to 'jack', if you want to feeed 1 pack to your pet immediately, say jack feed 1.
or you plan to feed 10 packs food to your pet at 21:00, you can say "jack feed 10 at 9 pm".
Note that: for better name recognition, please set the device name to one word first name，like 'jack'、‘mike’ 、‘jordon’ or other else。
